values: <font size="2" color="#00ccff">Ok so i thought this looked like fun..its not like anyone really will be reading it anyways so whatever. ha. well right now sucks. ive been at home for the past like 5 days.. i have freakin mono! i have no clue how i got it either. the doctor said it isnt spread from people or drinking or anything so who knows? but i guess its a good time to have it, all my friends are grounded or out of town. evan,heather,and annah all got drinking tickets the other night and the police called their house at 1 in the morning and their parents had to come and pick them up. stupid right? yeah well luckily me katie and spenser had a feeling it was going to get busted so we left just in time. and it wasnt even worth it, it was at some guys house we didnt even know. well i went home the next morning and i got caught in the middle of a huge lie so i had to tell the real story and my mom asked me if i had been drinking and i lied..but i knew she knew. how could she not? like seriously shes known forever, so i just went ahead and told her ive been drinking. it went well actually. im not in trouble except i cant drive for a month after my birthday. and i told her im not going to drink anymore, which i am going to try to keep my word. everyone says i cant which kind of upsets me but i guess its expected. anyways..i was thinking about it and i love mallory mason so much. seriously everytime i get myself into shit she is always there for me and takes up for me. shes one of the best friends ever :) and i miss hanging out with her,callie,elanor,amanda,britni and everyone else all the time. they are still my best friends, i just havent been seeing much of them lately. or atleast all of us in a big group. BUT on a brighter note, james is coming home soon! im excited and i miss him alot. and then after that i am going to oxford to see all of my friends that i havent seen in a year! i know it will be lots of fun, i am leaving the 11th and coming home the 22nd. and eleanor gets home the 21st so i will see her! and someone else is coming home around then, wont say who though. yeah but i am about to go to sleep, me and my mom are going to go to lunch tomorrow. i love her soo much. goodnight :)</font>
